data.description: Beautiful County home nestled on an over sized lot in the city of Hempstead. Public water, inside the established gated Community of Deerwood Lakes. Low property taxes, community pool, beautiful neighborhood lakes. This is an opportunity to get away from the city but still conveniently located near Highway 6, with easy access to Highway 290. ONLY 20 min from Prairie View, 30 min from Brenham, 30 min from Magnolia! This list price only includes one lot. The additional lot can be purchased together or seperately. the second lot includes a two car garage and storage shed.
